OL,6,FThe Easington Colliery Welfare trustee
OL,7,Fand volunteer remembers what life was
OL,8,Flike before the strike, and recalled
OL,9,Fhow "things changed overnight".
OL,11,FOnce bustling businesses shut up shop,
OL,12,Fpeople moved out and houses were left
OL,13,Fempty. These issues, he said, have
OL,14,Fnever been resolved.
OL,16,F"It doesn't matter which political
OL,17,Fparty's in power," he told ITV Tyne
OL,18,FTees. "The east coast of Durham has
OL,19,Fhad no investment whatsoever."
