OL,6,FEx-miner Stephen Fergus gives his
OL,7,Fperspective on how the strike changed
OL,8,Fhis village forever
OL,10,FBefore the strike and the ensuing
OL,11,Fcolliery closures - communities like
OL,12,Fthose in County Durham and
OL,13,FNorthumberland centred around mining
OL,14,Fwere flourishing.
