OL,6,FPaul Swinney, director of policy and
OL,7,Fresearch at independent think tank
OL,8,FCentre for Cities, said: "Mining was a
OL,9,Freally key exporting sector for the
OL,10,FNorth East. It's selling something to
OL,11,Fthe rest of the country, to the rest
OL,12,Fof the world.
OL,14,F"It's bringing money in which puts
OL,15,Fmoney in people's pockets so they can
OL,16,Fgo out and spend in the shops and the
OL,17,Fpubs etc.
OL,19,F"If you take that brick in the wall
OL,20,Fout then everything collapses around
OL,21,Fit."
