OL,6,FThe impact to this day is stark in
OL,7,Fsome of the latest government figures.
OL,9,FImpact in figures
OL,11,FThe percentage of children living in
OL,12,Flow income families in Easington,
OL,13,FBlackhall and Horden is between 25%
OL,14,Fand 30%.
OL,16,FThose figures, from the Department for
OL,17,FWork and Pensions from 2021 and 2022,
OL,18,Fcompare to the national average of 20%.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/14
