OL,6,FAccording to the 2021 census, the
OL,7,Famount of people in full time
OL,8,Femployment in these former coalfield
OL,9,Fareas is also much lower than the
OL,10,Fnational average of 34%.
OL,12,FIn the three communities that figure
OL,13,Fis between 26% and 31%.
OL,15,FAnd there is still a skills shortage
OL,16,Fin the area. Census figures from 2021
OL,17,Fshow the number of people aged over 16
OL,18,Fwith no qualifications is between 26%
OL,19,Fand 32%.
