OL,6,FThat is compared to a national average
OL,7,Fof just 18%.
OL,9,FThe communities hit the hardest were
OL,10,Fthose that were totally dependent on
OL,11,Fthe mines.
OL,13,FMr Swinney attributes the North East's
OL,14,Fstruggle over the decades to the
OL,15,Funderperformance of cities in
OL,16,Fproducing employment opportunities for
OL,17,Fthose living as far out as the
OL,18,Fcoalfields.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/14
