OL,4,Cand '40 years of pain' for North East
OL,6,F"The real issue for the North East
OL,7,Feconomy and the reason why it
OL,8,Fstruggled over the last 30 to 40 years
OL,9,Fisn't just the closure of industry,"
OL,10,Fhe continued.
OL,12,F"That clearly was a blow (but) it was
OL,13,Fthe ability of cities in particular to
OL,14,Fgenerate the jobs and more high paid
OL,15,Factivities as the UK economy moved
OL,16,Ftowards that."
OL,18,FMr Swinney also credits the failure of
OL,19,Fthe region to bounce back with the
OL,20,Fnature of the approach to regeneration.
