OL,6,F"We've had pits on certain sites and
OL,7,Fthe pit has closed and I think there's
OL,8,Fbeen a bit of a mindset that
OL,9,Fsomething's been there before, so
OL,10,Fsomething must go on that direct site
OL,11,Fonce again," he explained.
OL,13,FThis, he said, resulted in building
OL,14,Foffice blocks on former pit sites and
OL,15,Fout of town developments which
OL,16,Freplaced one set of low skilled jobs
OL,17,Fwith other low skilled jobs.
