OL,6,FThere was still "hope" for the North
OL,7,FEast with current developments and
OL,8,Finvestment in Newcastle and Sunderland
OL,9,Fwhich could bring high value jobs.
OL,11,FHope is also provided by organisations
OL,12,Fworking to help improve communities
OL,13,Flike Horden.
OL,15,FAmong them is the Coalfields
OL,16,FRegeneration Trust. Paula Snowdon,
OL,17,Fregional development manager, is
OL,18,Fworking to combat challenges faced by
OL,19,Fthose who live there.
