OL,6,FShe told ITV Tyne Tees the loss of
OL,7,Findustry could still be seen today
OL,8,Fwith "employment challenges, health
OL,9,Fchallenges, skills shortages and
OL,10,F(poor) transport links" affecting the
OL,11,Fregion.
OL,13,F"We've now got a lot of teams on the
OL,14,Fground who can respond to those
OL,15,Fchallenges and we're moving in the
OL,16,Fright direction," she added.
OL,18,FThe organisation works to create
OL,19,Fopportunities for coalfield
OL,20,Fcommunities, improve health, skills
OL,21,Fand employment.
