OL,6,FAt East Durham College, the area's
OL,7,Fheritage is not forgotten but the
OL,8,Ffocus is on the future.
OL,10,FThe college began as a miners'
OL,11,Ftraining college, offering the
OL,12,FNational Certificate in Mining, but it
OL,13,Fhas had to reinvent itself. Now, more
OL,14,Fthan 7,000 students study everything
OL,15,Ffrom music to IT.
