OL,6,FCarina Tomlinson, vice principle,
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are one of the few colleges
OL,8,Fthat offer all 15 subject sector
OL,9,Fareas, so we have a great breadth of
OL,10,Foffer in this college because for us
OL,11,Fit's about social mobility, and not
OL,12,Fjust employment, (but) to go on to
OL,13,Funiversity and do things that they may
OL,14,Fbe the first person in their family to
OL,15,Fdo.
OL,17,F"There are a lot of minimum wage jobs
OL,18,Faround the area but we want our
OL,19,Fstudents to aspire to better than
OL,20,Fthat."
